## การสร้าง Display Text เบื้องต้น
---

#### Syntax
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
display.newText( [parentGroup,] text, x, y, font [, fontSize] )
display.newText( [parentGroup,] text, x, y [, width, height], font [, fontSize] )
</pre>

---

<br/>



## Single-Line Text
---

[![ภาพแสดง ผลลัพธ์ของการสร้าง Single-Line Text][7]](){: .fancybox-button 
               data-fancybox-group="display-text-001"
               href="<%= current_page.data.baseURL %>images/categories/Corona SDK/display-text-001.png"}

#### Single-Line Text (Example-01)
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
local myText = display.newText( "Hello World!", 100, 200, native.systemFont, 30 )
myText:setFillColor( 1, 0, 0 )
</pre>

<br/>

#### Single-Line Text (Example-02)
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
local myText = display.newText( "Hello World!", <mark>display.contentCenterX</mark>, <mark>display.contentCenterY</mark>, native.systemFont, 30 )
myText:setFillColor( 1, 0, 0 )
</pre>

<br/>

#### Single-Line Text (Example-03)
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
local myText = display.newText( "Hello World!", display.contentCenterX, display.contentCenterY, native.systemFont, 30 )
myText:setFillColor( 1, 0, 0 )
<mark>myText.anchorX = 1</mark>
</pre>

