## Multi-Line Text
---

[![ภาพแสดง ผลลัพธ์ของการสร้าง Multi-Line Text][8]](){: .fancybox-button 
               data-fancybox-group="display-text-002"
               href="<%= current_page.data.baseURL %>images/categories/Corona SDK/display-text-002.png"}

#### Multi-Line Text  (Example-04)
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
-- Create first multi-line text object
local options1 = 
{
    text = "The quick brown fox jumped over the lazy dog.",
    y = 100,
    x = 130,
    <mark>align = "left"</mark>,-- default : left
    width = 200,     --required for multi-line and alignment
    font = native.systemFont,
    fontSize = 18
}
local myText1 = display.newText( options1 )
myText1:setFillColor( 1, 0, 0 )
</pre>


<br/>

